DESCRIPTION
------------



BUILD
------

# requires maven 3
mvn package


INSTALLATION
-------------

# sphelios command line tool
aptitude install spotify-helios-cli

# helios server
aptitude install spotify-helios-server


DEVELOPING
----------

Prerequisites:

* docker listening on port 4160 on localhost. For local development a Vagrantfile is provided which will setup a VM running Docker appropriately.
